data.description: Short Sale. GREAT OPPORTUNITY TO OWN THIS LOVELY 3 BEDROOM/2 BATH HOME IN FAIRWAYS OF QUAIL HOLLOW! STEP INSIDE AND YOU WILL FIND VAULTED CEILINGS IN THE SPACIOUS LIVING ROOM/DINING ROOM WITH BEAUTIFUL BAMBOO FLOORING. KITCHEN HAS PLENTY OF CABINETS, UPGRADED APPLIANCES AND A COZY BREAKFAST NOOK. THE LARGE MASTER SUITE FEATURES A WALK-IN CLOSET AND MASTER BATH WITH A GARDEN TUB, SEPARATE SHOWER AND DUAL VANITY. THIS SPLIT FLOOR PLAN COMES WITH TWO ADDITIONAL BEDROOMS AND 2ND FULL BATH. UPGRADES INCLUDE ROOF INSTALLED IN 2020, H/W HEATER 2019, A/C 2016 AND EXTERIOR PAINTED 2023. NO NEED TO BRING YOUR LAWN MOWER! YOUR HOA INCLUDES LAWN CARE, EXTERIOR PAINTING & PEST CONTROL! LOW HOA AND NO CDD FEES. CONVENIENTLY LOCATED JUST MINUTES TO SHOPS, RESTAURANTS, TAMPA OUTLETS, WIREGRASS MALL AND I75. EASY COMMUTE TO  DOWNTOWN TAMPA, USF & VA HOSPITAL.
